# Documentation

This folder contains public-safe documentation for the Agentic Sales Orchestrator reference implementation.

Do not upload secrets, tenant-private data, real customer records, passwords, tokens, API keys, or confidential implementation details.

## Key documents

| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `architecture/ASO_Architecture_and_Delivery_Model.md` | Target architecture, delivery roadmap, phase model, trial MVP overlay, and operating principle. |
| `architecture/ASO_Operations_Testing_ALM_and_Release_Gates.md` | Observability, testing, ALM, customer-ready checklist, and approval gates. |
| `standards/ASO_Project_Wide_Naming_and_Creation_Standard.md` | Naming and creation standard for all component families. |
| `decisions/ASO_Phase1_Completion_and_Deferred_Items.md` | Phase 1 completion record and deferred-items register. |
| `risks/ASO_Risks_Assumptions_and_Controls.md` | Risk register, assumptions, controls, and customer-ready checklist. |

